      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows expected wear for its age. The exterior has several visible scuffs, a few small dings, and the clear coat is beginning to fade on the roof and hood. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows some staining and minor wear on the driver's seat bolster. Mechanically, the car runs and drives well, though the suspension is starting to feel a bit loose and it will likely need new tires and a brake service within the next few thousand miles. It is a solid, functional option for someone looking for dependable transportation who isn't concerned with cosmetic perfection.",
