    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_8_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "Looking for a diamond in the rough? This vehicle is the perfect project for a mechanical enthusiast or someone looking for a budget-friendly fixer-upper! While it currently requires significant mechanical work and has some visible wear and tear, it offers a great foundation for someone ready to roll up their sleeves and bring it back to life.",
