      "description": "Presented in exemplary condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Every detail, from the flawless coachwork to the meticulously maintained interior, reflects an uncompromising standard of care. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a specimen of peerless mechanical and aesthetic integrity, perfectly suited for the most sophisticated collector.",
