    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade E46 M3, showcasing the pinnacle of the S54B32 naturally aspirated inline-six. This example features a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a factory-spec M Variable Differential Lock. Mechanically flawless, the VANOS system has been professionally bulletproofed, and the rear subframe has undergone proactive reinforcement to ensure peak structural rigidity. The chassis retains its factory-fresh damping characteristics, while the throttle response from the individual throttle bodies remains razor-sharp. With zero oxidation on the undercarriage and a paint meter-verified exterior, this is a turn-key collector piece for the discerning purist.",
